---
/**
 * src/pages/about.astro — About Haynes Industrial Medicine
 */

import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Haynes Industrial Medicine"
  description="Haynes Industrial Medicine provides DOT drug testing, respirator fit testing, and CPR/AED training for industrial workforces. Learn about our background and approach."
>
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-brand-900 dark:text-white">About Us</h1>

    <div class="prose-content mt-8">
      <p>
        Haynes Industrial Medicine exists because we've seen what happens when
        compliance testing and safety training are treated as an afterthought —
        or when a clinic that doesn't understand industrial work is handling your
        workforce's requirements.
      </p>

      <p>
        The Haynes family has been in industrial operations for over fifteen years.
        We've managed crews, navigated OSHA audits, and dealt with the real
        pressure of keeping a workforce productive and compliant at the same time.
        That background shapes how we operate.
      </p>

      <h2>What We're Focused On</h2>
      <p>
        We're building this practice around three services industrial employers
        need regularly and need done right:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>DOT Drug Testing</strong> — DOT-compliant urine drug screens
          for regulated employers. Pre-employment, random, post-accident, and
          reasonable suspicion. MRO review included.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Respirator Fit Testing</strong> — OSHA-required quantitative
          and qualitative fit testing for tight-fitting respirators, with proper
          documentation for your records.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>CPR/AED Training</strong> — Certification courses for
          individuals and work groups, scheduled around your operation and
          conducted at your facility when that's easier.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        We're growing deliberately. Our focus right now is on doing these three
        things exceptionally well — not on being everything to everyone.
      </p>

      <h2>How We Work</h2>
      <p>
        We keep things simple. Same-day drug testing is almost always available.
        Fit testing and CPR/AED training can be scheduled around your shifts — and
        we'll come to your facility when that works better. Documentation goes
        directly to your safety team, ready for your files.
      </p>
      <p>
        We're not a volume clinic. We're a small operation that takes the time to
        understand your compliance program and your schedule.
      </p>

      <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
      <p>
        Ready to set up testing or schedule a training? <a href="/contact">Contact us</a>
        or give us a call. We'll figure out what you need and get it done.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
